{"tid":2077203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】巴西成全球疫情第二嚴重國家 美七州住院確診者創新高","createTime":"2020-06-24T06:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T06:11:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"426e42150863d01e70195b013c577e438e5e0437","tid":2077203,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"最新霍普金斯大學數字顯示，巴西周三新增 3.94 萬人確診感染武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) ，令該國累積超過 114.5 萬宗確診感染，逾 5.26 萬人病死，成為成全球疫情第二嚴重國家。許多專家認為，該國缺乏病毒測試，僅是所需的二十分之一，表明感染數字可能比官方更高。<br />\n<br />\n巴西法官下令博爾索納羅戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統博爾索納羅 (Jair Bolsonaro) 被指是該國疫情變得嚴峻的問題所在，該國多地都有反博爾索納羅的示威。博爾索納羅多次要求各州盡快解禁重啟經濟，又在出席公開活動時並無戴上口罩。周一有法官下令爾索納羅在首都巴西利亞出席活動時戴口罩，指任何人包括總統並不能凌駕聯邦法例，如他再次被發現無戴口罩，將每日罰款 2,000 里奧罰款（折合約 3,010 港元）；該國在四月尾已頒佈法例外出時必須戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n法官 Renato Coelho Borelli 表明，總統需採取所有必須措施避免 COVID-19 的傳播，不單是保護其自身健康，也為其周圍人著想。 Borelli 又在判詞中指，簡單在 Google 搜尋已找到多張爾索納羅在首都以及周邊地區無載口罩的相片，令其他人曝露於疫情蔓延威脅之下，而疫情蔓延已引起全國性的動盪⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%88%90%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%83%E5%B7%9E%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=796ecd6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&h=28d91f17\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E6%88%90%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%83%E5%B7%9E%E4%BD%8F%E9%99%A2%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/</a>"},{"pid":"50a872545183fbb77f381a7601c393f9bbeac809","tid":2077203,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bee46cfde763093d7a880bc48374320445b0ab6b","tid":2077203,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:11:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全球第一</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}